@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### 1. Register User (Driver)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Driver",
  "email": "john@spotsync.com",
  "password": "securePassword123",
  "role": "driver"
}

### 2. Register Admin User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Admin",
  "email": "jane@spotsync.com",
  "password": "securePassword123",
  "role": "admin"
}

### 3. Login as Admin (To get token)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane@spotsync.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

### 4. Create Parking Zone (Admin Only - Replace Bearer token with the token from Step 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/zones
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "name": "Terminal 1 EV Charging",
  "type": "ev_charging",
  "total_capacity": 20,
  "price_per_hour": 5.50
}

### 5. Get All Zones (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/zones

### 6. Get Single Zone (Public - Replace with actual zone UUID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/zones/<ZONE_UUID_HERE>

### 7. Update Parking Zone (Admin Only - Replace Bearer token and UUID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/zones/<ZONE_UUID_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "name": "Terminal 1 EV Charging (Updated)",
  "type": "ev_charging",
  "total_capacity": 25,
  "price_per_hour": 6.50
}

### 8. Delete Parking Zone (Admin Only - Replace Bearer token and UUID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/zones/<ZONE_UUID_HERE>
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>

### 9. Login as Driver
# @name loginDriver
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@spotsync.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

### 10. Get Driver Profile (Protected - Replace Bearer token with token from Step 9)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <DRIVER_TOKEN_HERE>

### 11. Make a Reservation (Driver - Replace Bearer token and zone_id with actual UUID values)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reservations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <DRIVER_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "zone_id": "<ZONE_UUID_HERE>",
  "license_plate": "ABC-1234"
}

### 12. Get My Reservations (Driver - Replace Bearer token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reservations/my-reservations
Authorization: Bearer <DRIVER_TOKEN_HERE>

### 13. Cancel Reservation (Driver - Replace Bearer token and reservation UUID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reservations/<RESERVATION_UUID_HERE>
Authorization: Bearer <DRIVER_TOKEN_HERE>

### 14. Get All Reservations (Admin Only - Replace Bearer token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/reservations
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>
